<plot>This is a promotional short film for _The Moonshine War (1970)_ . It shows filming on location in an unidentified rural setting, beginning with the arrival of the large MGM equipment trucks. The narrator, who says he is one of the local residents, provides commentary as we see two car chases filmed. The film's director and five of main actors are shown at work.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?494220</url></doc>
